quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  8,34,"Uye zvingagona sei kuti Allah vasavarange ivo vachirambidza (vanhu) kuAl-Masjid Al-Haraam, uye havazi vachengeti vayo? Hakuna anokwanisa kuve muchengeti wayo kunze kweavo vanotya (Allah), asi vazhinji vavo havazvizivi"
  8,35,"Uye munamato wavo (Swalaah) muimba (yaAllah, Ka’bah) pakanga pasina zviripo asi mheterwa nekuombera maoko. Naizvozvo ravirai murango nokuda kwekuti makanga musingatendi"
  8,36,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vasingatendi vanoshandisa hupfumi hwavo kudzivirira (vanhu) kufamba munzira yaAllah, uye vacharamba vachiushandisa, asi mhedzisiro yacho huchava musengwa kwavari. Uye vachakurirwa, uye avo vasingatendi kuGehena ndiko kwavachaunganidzwa"
  8,37,"Kuitira kuti Allah vagosiyanisa vakaipa (vasingatendi uye vanoita zvakaipa) kubva mune vakanaka (vanotenda muIslaam uye vanoita zvakanaka), uye vagoisa vaipi, umwe pamusoro peumwe, vovaunganidza pamwechete, uye vovakanda muGehena. Ivavo, ndivo vanhu vakarasikirwa"
  8,38,"Iti kune avo vasingatendi: “Kana vakasiya (Kusatenda), zvitadzo zvavo zvekare zvinoregererwa. Asi kana vakadzokera (muKusatenda) zvino muenzaniso weavo (vakarangwa) mushure mavo wakatodarika (seyambiro).”"
  8,39,"Uye varwisei kusvikira pasisina Fitnah (Kusatenda) uye chitendero chava chaAllah chete (pasi rese). Asi kana vakasiya (Kusatenda), zvino, muzvokwadi Allah ndivo vanoona zvizere zvavanoita"
  8,40,"Uye kana vakafuratira, zvino chiziva kuti Allah ndivo muchengeti wako. Muchengeti akanaka uye mubetseri ane hunyanzvi"